      <li><strong>Dye test plus paper towel trace.</strong> Practitioner-grade diagnostic, not guesswork.</li>
      <li><strong>Floor and cabinetry protection on every visit.</strong> Standard practice.</li>
      <li><strong>Brand-specific gasket knowledge.</strong> Bosch 6-piece kits, Miele continuous seals, Whirlpool/KitchenAid shared platform.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS Licensed #A49573 and EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$89 residential diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/not-draining/">dishwasher not draining</a>, <a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/not-cleaning/">dishwasher not cleaning</a>, <a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/error-codes/">dishwasher error codes</a>. Parent: <a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/">residential dishwasher repair pillar</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 09 FAQ -->
<section class="section">
